column5: Well it was another 40+ fish day!   like i said before, here's the other report!!  man they have been on fire, we have been putting a beating on them.... just hope we can get out a couple more times before ice!!!!  here are a couple of the nicer ones....  enjoy the pics everyone!      and no this is not the same pic.... it's another pic of jay double fisting big eyes...hahahahha
Nice catch !!!!!...love those big fall eyes...cheers
